WEBVTT

00:01:29.163 --> 00:01:30.805
and breaks down.

00:01:32.886 --> 00:01:34.438
Alex loved Amanda.

00:01:35.088 --> 00:01:38.243
And he was one of the most
honorable men on earth,

00:01:38.267 --> 00:01:40.319
and at the age of 24,

00:01:41.376 --> 00:01:45.135
he had to make the decision
to risk his life

00:01:45.159 --> 00:01:47.791
in order to ensure she would live.

00:01:49.298 --> 00:01:52.914
I knew in my heart if he couldn't get up,

00:01:54.486 --> 00:01:55.867
he was dead.

00:01:58.890 --> 00:02:00.176
I had just arrived